        {
            "title": "恒生私有化｜恒生半日報150.3元仲有水位？滙豐「未止瀉」連跌兩日(更新)",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"恒生私有化｜恒生獲滙豐提私有化，股價初段飆逾四成。(資料圖片)\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"587\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rN3hRMJN7ToBSwfm709gwg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU4NztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/no/am730_578/b1695150e550745829a1e930c64f6693\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">恒生私有化｜恒生獲滙豐提私有化，股價初段飆逾四成。(資料圖片)</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>【10月10日更新】</strong>滙豐控股(005)昨日宣布以每股155元私有化<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:恒生銀行;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/恒生銀行\">恒生銀行</a>(011)，計劃完成後將撤銷恒生逾50年的上市地位。此重磅消息震撼市場，恒生股價昨日急升，而滙豐股價則應聲下挫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">至於今日半日市況持續反映此趨勢。恒生銀行股價靠穩，半日升0.33%，報150.3元，與155元的收購價相比，仍存在約3.1%的潛在上升空間。相反，滙豐則「未止瀉」，股價再跌0.48%，報103.5元，連續第二日受壓。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4ddc80af-953d-38c4-aa3a-44448837a96f-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大市方面，恒生指數連跌第五日，今早一度急跌近400點，再度失守20天線。恒指低開228點後，跌幅擴大至391點，低見26,360點。中午收市報26,447點，跌304點或1.14%，成交額達1,803.26億元。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\">恒生私有化｜恒生初段升逾40%高見168元 滙豐急插逾6% (更新)</h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>【10月9日更新】</strong>恒指半日走勢反覆，後靠穩。恒指高開32點，隨後轉跌381點，低見26,480點，其後走勢回穩，恒生指數半日反升11點，報26,840點，大市半日成交2,073億元；國企指數指數升49點，報9,573點；恒生科技指數升41點，報6,555點。滙豐(005)，跌6.24%，報103.7元；恒生(011)曾高見168元，升26.3%，報150.3元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>港股高開32點，恒生指數26,862點，</span></span></span></span></span>最新報26,599點，跌227點，大市成交996億元；國企指數9,478點，跌44點；恒生科技指數6,461點，跌50點。<span><span><span><span><span>其中</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>滙豐銀行(005)建議</span></span></span></span></span>以每股現金155元將恒生銀行(011)私有化，較恒生上日收市價119元溢價三成，恒生將會撤銷53年的上市地位。受到消息影響，滙豐及恒生股價走勢各異。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">其中恒生銀行股價今早大幅高開近15%，報<span><span><span><span><span>136.8元，初段一度高見168元，較昨日119</span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span>收市價抽升逾四成，成交27.06億元。</span></span></span></span></span>最新報150.4元，升26%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span><span>至於滙豐銀行(005)則低開3%，開報107.5元，截至發稿，滙豐初段跌逾6%，報103.6元，成交24.77億元。</span></span></span></span></span></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">滙豐銀行及恒生銀行今早發聯合公告，表示滙豐亞太作為要約人，已要求恒生銀行董事會向計劃股東提呈建議，以協議安排方式將恒生銀行私有化，持有恒生銀行的股東，每股可獲現金155元，較恒生銀行昨日收市價119元溢價約30%。私有化完成後，恒生銀行將會撤銷上市地位。</p><h3 class=\"mb-module-gap text-px20 font-bold lg:text-px18 text-batcave\">資料來源：<a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:滙豐及恒生公告;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2025/1009/2025100900166_c.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">滙豐及恒生公告</a></h3><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文刊登於 AM730 <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/恒生私有化-恒生半日報150.3元仲有水位-滙豐-未止瀉-連跌兩日-更新-/606889?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/恒生私有化-恒生半日報150.3元仲有水位-滙豐-未止瀉-連跌兩日-更新-/606889?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/財經/恒生私有化-恒生半日報150.3元仲有水位-滙豐-未止瀉-連跌兩日-更新-/606889?utm_source=yahoorss&amp;utm_medium=referral</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%81%92%E7%94%9F%E7%A7%81%E6%9C%89%E5%8C%96-%E6%81%92%E7%94%9F%E5%88%9D%E6%AE%B5%E5%8D%87%E9%80%BE40-%E9%AB%98%E8%A6%8B168%E5%85%83-%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90%E6%80%A5%E6%8F%92%E9%80%BE6-013938975.html",
